sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as API Client
    participant Gateway as vllm-orchestrator-gateway<br/>8090/TCP HTTP
    participant Orchestrator as FMS Guardrails Orchestrator<br/>8085/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Detectors as Content Detectors<br/>(e.g., regex-detector)
    participant vLLM as vLLM Model Server

    Note over Client,vLLM: Flow 1: Non-Streaming Chat Completion with Content Detection

    Client->>Gateway: POST /{route}/v1/chat/completions<br/>Authorization: Bearer token<br/>stream: false
    Note over Gateway: Load route config<br/>Inject detector specs<br/>into payload
    Gateway->>Orchestrator: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>Authorization forwarded<br/>x-forwarded-* headers<br/>Optional mTLS client cert
    Orchestrator->>Detectors: Input content detection
    Detectors-->>Orchestrator: Detection results
    Orchestrator->>vLLM: Inference request
    vLLM-->>Orchestrator: Model response
    Orchestrator->>Detectors: Output content detection
    Detectors-->>Orchestrator: Detection results
    Orchestrator-->>Gateway: JSON response with detections
    Note over Gateway: Check detections<br/>If detected + fallback configured:<br/>replace content with fallback msg
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON response<br/>(original or fallback)

    Note over Client,vLLM: Flow 2: Streaming Chat Completion with Content Detection (SSE)

    Client->>Gateway: POST /{route}/v1/chat/completions<br/>Authorization: Bearer token<br/>stream: true
    Note over Gateway: Load route config<br/>Inject detector specs
    Gateway->>Orchestrator: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>stream: true<br/>Optional mTLS
    Orchestrator->>Detectors: Input content detection
    Detectors-->>Orchestrator: Detection results
    Orchestrator->>vLLM: Streaming inference
    loop SSE chunks
        vLLM-->>Orchestrator: SSE chunk
        Orchestrator->>Detectors: Per-chunk output detection
        Detectors-->>Orchestrator: Detection result
        Orchestrator-->>Gateway: SSE data: chunk
        Note over Gateway: Parse SSE chunk<br/>Apply fallback per-chunk<br/>if detection found
        Gateway-->>Client: SSE data: chunk<br/>(original or fallback)
    end
    Gateway-->>Client: SSE data: [DONE]
